<h2>About</h2>
<p>Flames is a fun and interactive app that allows you to discover the compatibility and potential future with your crush or partner. Enter your names, and Flames will reveal the connection between you based on the acronym 'FLAMES' (Friends, Lovers, Affectionate, Marriage, Enemies, Siblings). Uncover the exciting possibilities and deepen your understanding of your relationship dynamics with this entertaining and light-hearted Flames app.</p>
